#: app/templates/rules.html:8
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr "So funktioniert's"

#: app/templates/rules.html:10
msgid "Predict the final score for each match <strong>before kickoff</strong>."
msgstr "Sage das Endergebnis jedes Spiels <strong>vor Anpfiff</strong> voraus."

#: app/templates/rules.html:11
msgid ""
"For knockout matches, if you predict a draw, you must also pick the "
"<strong>penalty shootout winner</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Bei K.o.-Spielen musst du bei einem Unentschieden auch den "
"<strong>Elfmeterschießen-Gewinner</strong> wählen."

#: app/templates/rules.html:12
msgid ""
"Once a match kicks off, your prediction is <strong>locked</strong> and "
"visible to other players."
msgstr ""
"Nach Anpfiff wird dein Tipp <strong>gesperrt</strong> und für andere "
"Spieler sichtbar."

#: app/templates/rules.html:13
msgid "Points are awarded automatically when results are entered."
msgstr "Punkte werden automatisch vergeben, wenn Ergebnisse eingetragen werden."

#: app/templates/rules.html:18
msgid "Scoring"
msgstr "Punktevergabe"

#: app/templates/rules.html:24
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Beispiel"

#: app/templates/rules.html:29
msgid "Correct winner"
msgstr "Richtiger Sieger"

#: app/templates/rules.html:30 app/templates/rules.html:40
msgid "1 pt"
msgstr "1 Pkt"

#: app/templates/rules.html:31
msgid "Match: 2-0 — You predicted: 1-0"
msgstr "Spiel: 2-0 — Dein Tipp: 1-0"

#: app/templates/rules.html:34
msgid "Exact score"
msgstr "Genaues Ergebnis"

#: app/templates/rules.html:35 app/templates/rules.html:45
msgid "3 pts"
msgstr "3 Pkt"

#: app/templates/rules.html:36
msgid "Match: 2-1 — You predicted: 2-1"
msgstr "Spiel: 2-1 — Dein Tipp: 2-1"

#: app/templates/rules.html:39
msgid "Correct draw"
msgstr "Richtiges Unentschieden"

#: app/templates/rules.html:41
msgid "Match: 1-1 — You predicted: 0-0"
msgstr "Spiel: 1-1 — Dein Tipp: 0-0"

#: app/templates/rules.html:44
msgid "Exact draw"
msgstr "Genaues Unentschieden"

#: app/templates/rules.html:46
msgid "Match: 1-1 — You predicted: 1-1"
msgstr "Spiel: 1-1 — Dein Tipp: 1-1"

#: app/templates/rules.html:49
msgid "Penalty winner bonus (knockout only)"
msgstr "Elfmeter-Gewinner-Bonus (nur K.o.-Runde)"

#: app/templates/rules.html:50
msgid "+1 pt"
msgstr "+1 Pkt"

#: app/templates/rules.html:51
msgid "You correctly predicted who advances on penalties"
msgstr "Du hast richtig getippt, wer im Elfmeterschießen weiterkommt"

#: app/templates/rules.html:55
msgid "Maximum per match: 4 points"
msgstr "Maximum pro Spiel: 4 Punkte"

#: app/templates/rules.html:55
msgid "(exact draw + penalty bonus in knockout)"
msgstr "(genaues Unentschieden + Elfmeter-Bonus in der K.o.-Runde)"

#: app/templates/rules.html:59
msgid "Which Score Counts?"
msgstr "Welches Ergebnis zählt?"

#: app/templates/rules.html:61
msgid "Group stage:"
msgstr "Gruppenphase:"

#: app/templates/rules.html:61
msgid "Full-time score (90 minutes)."
msgstr "Endergebnis (90 Minuten)."

#: app/templates/rules.html:62
msgid "Knockout stage:"
msgstr "K.o.-Runde:"

#: app/templates/rules.html:62
msgid ""
"After Extra Time (AET) score if extra time was played, otherwise the "
"90-minute score. The penalty shootout determines who advances but does "
"not change the match score."
msgstr ""
"Ergebnis nach Verlängerung (n.V.), falls Verlängerung gespielt wurde, "
"ansonsten das 90-Minuten-Ergebnis. Das Elfmeterschießen bestimmt, wer "
"weiterkommt, ändert aber nicht das Spielergebnis."

#: app/templates/rules.html:67
msgid "Important"
msgstr "Wichtig"

#: app/templates/rules.html:69
msgid "Predictions must be submitted <strong>before the match kicks off</strong>."
msgstr "Tipps müssen <strong>vor Anpfiff</strong> abgegeben werden."

#: app/templates/rules.html:70
msgid "You can update your predictions as many times as you want before kickoff."
msgstr "Du kannst deine Tipps vor Anpfiff beliebig oft ändern."

#: app/templates/rules.html:71
msgid "Other players' predictions are <strong>hidden until kickoff</strong>."
msgstr "Tipps anderer Spieler sind <strong>bis zum Anpfiff verborgen</strong>."

#: app/templates/rules.html:72
msgid "The leaderboard updates in real time as results come in."
msgstr "Die Rangliste wird in Echtzeit aktualisiert, wenn Ergebnisse eintreffen."

